AddressInfo.Title: Centralia Supercharger
AddressInfo.AccessComments: From I-5 N   :  Take exit 82 for Harrison Ave;  Turn left onto Harrison Ave;  Turn right onto Belmont Ave;  Take the 1st right onto Haviland St;  Haviland St turns left and becomes Lum Rd;  Supercharger will be on your right.  /  From I-5S  : Take exit 82 for Harrison Avenue;  Keep right at the fork, follow signs for Harrison Ave and merge onto Harrison Ave; Turn right onto Belmont Ave;  Take the 1st right onto Haviland St;  Haviland St turns left and becomes Lum Rd;   Supercharger will be on your right.
